      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized variable valve timing. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring precise power delivery to the rear wheels. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate chassis fatigue and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing. The suspension maintains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, while the four-piston braking system provides consistent thermal management. Though the exterior displays minor patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
